edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations

Annotation Type MMethodRef


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MMethodRef
    Annotation interface for method reference. Bound to the field holding the exposed method reference, which is the original method name.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String methodName
      Actual name of method.
      String name
      Original name of method, exposed as a field holding a method reference.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        Original name of method, exposed as a field holding a method reference. This may not be the same as the real method name.

      • methodName

        public abstract String methodName
        Actual name of method.
